OL,3,CWho is Robert Aramayo: Hull-born actor
OL,4,Ctakes home two BAFTA's
OL,6,FDespite a resume featuring Game of
OL,7,FThrones and The Rings of Power, Robert
OL,8,FAramayo, BAFTA's latest crowned Rising
OL,9,FStar and Best Actor, remains
OL,10,Frelatively under-the-radar.
OL,12,FThe 33-year-old was recognised at the
OL,13,F79th British Academy Film Awards
OL,14,Fceremony on Sunday following his
OL,15,Fportrayal of Scottish campaigner for
OL,16,FTourette syndrome John Davidson in the
OL,17,Fbiopic I Swear.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/8
