OL,3,CWho is Robert Aramayo: Hull-born actor
OL,4,Ctakes home two BAFTA's
OL,6,FSo, who is the man who defeated
OL,7,FHollywood heavyweights, including
OL,8,FLeonardo DiCaprio, Ethan Hawke and
OL,9,FTimothee Chalamet?
OL,11,FBorn and raised in Hull, Aramayo's
OL,12,Fjourney began at the Hull Truck Youth
OL,13,FTheatre, which he joined at age ten.
OL,14,FAfter performing there throughout his
OL,15,Fchildhood, he secured a coveted place
OL,16,Fat the Juilliard School in New York
OL,17,FCity in 2011.
OL,26,@qD@Grr
