OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1771868901
OL,3,CWho is Robert Aramayo: Hull-born actor
OL,4,Ctakes home two BAFTA's
OL,6,FHis first major break came in 2016,
OL,7,Fplaying the role of a young Eddard
OL,8,FStark in seasons six and seven of Game
OL,9,Fof Thrones.
OL,11,FFrom there, he picked up acting
OL,12,Fcredits in the HBO miniseries Lewis
OL,13,Fand Clark and in 2020 was cast as
OL,14,F'Elrond' in Amazon's television series
OL,15,FThe Lord of the Rings: The Rings of
OL,16,FPower.
OL,18,FHowever, it is his role in I Swear
OL,19,Fthat has sparked a wave of critical
OL,20,Facclaim.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
