OL,3,CWho is Robert Aramayo: Hull-born actor
OL,4,Ctakes home two BAFTA's
OL,6,FThe biopic, directed, written and
OL,7,Fproduced by Kirk Jones, follows the
OL,8,Ftrue life story of John Davidson, a
OL,9,FScottish man with severe tourette
OL,10,Fsyndrome.
OL,12,FThe film follows Davidson's life as he
OL,13,Fgrows up in Galashiels, in the
OL,14,FScottish Borders, when he starts to
OL,15,Fexperience tics at age 12.
OL,17,FAccording to the NHS, Tourette
OL,18,Fsyndrome is a condition that causes
OL,19,Fyou to make sudden, repetitive sounds
OL,20,For movements (tics). There is no cure,
OL,21,Fbut treatment can help manage the tics.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
