OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1771868901
OL,3,CWho is Robert Aramayo: Hull-born actor
OL,4,Ctakes home two BAFTA's
OL,6,FI Swear also won the Bafta for best
OL,7,Fcasting.
OL,9,FAccepting the prize, he said: "This is
OL,10,Freally scary, last time I was at BAFTA
OL,11,FI dropped the award, so hopefully this
OL,12,Fwill go better."
OL,14,FHe added: "I can't believe this, it
OL,15,Freally blows my mind.
OL,17,F"John Davidson is the most remarkable
OL,18,Fperson I've ever met and he believes
OL,19,Fthere is so much more we need to learn
OL,20,Fabout Tourette's."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
