SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1771868901
OL,3,CWho is Robert Aramayo: Hull-born actor
OL,4,Ctakes home two BAFTA's
OL,6,F"In the words of the film, they need
OL,7,Fsupport and understanding."
OL,9,FHe continued: "This means the world to
OL,10,Fme, I can't believe it."
OL,12,FHe also included a special mention in
OL,13,Fhis speech to fellow actor Ethan Hawke.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
