PN,36607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1771868901
OL,3,CWho is Robert Aramayo: Hull-born actor
OL,4,Ctakes home two BAFTA's
OL,6,FHe said: "When I was in school, Ethan
OL,7,FHawke came in to speak to us at
OL,8,FJuilliard and he gave an amazing talk
OL,9,Fon longevity as an actor, about
OL,10,Fprotecting your instrument and
OL,11,Favoiding self-destructive behaviours,
OL,12,Fand it had a great impact on everyone
OL,13,Fin the room.
OL,15,F"So to be in this category with you
OL,16,Ftonight is incredible. Thank you
OL,17,FEthan."
OL,26,@nD@JOUwD@AOUyD@GO]
