OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1771868901
OL,3,CWho is Robert Aramayo: Hull-born actor
OL,4,Ctakes home two BAFTA's
OL,6,FAramayo joins previous recipients,
OL,7,Fincluding Sex Education star Emma
OL,8,FMackey, Get Out actor Daniel Kaluuya,
OL,9,FBlack Panther's Letitia Wright and
OL,10,FSpiderman actor Tom Holland.
OL,12,FHis portrayal of Davidson also won the
OL,13,Factor the British Independent Film
OL,14,FAward (BIFA) for best lead
OL,15,Fperformance, beating Cillian Murphy
OL,16,Fand Jennifer Lawrence.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/8
